{"tid":492064,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉自高登41J巴打] 有無人願意面對連登的真相","createTime":"2017-12-07T06:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T03:55:53.000Z","uid":32826,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e29c042d4da715e63c20b60200f5704cb2dbae3","tid":492064,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人禽之辨　在於明辨是非</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連尼住你隻孽畜，望之不似人棍！<br />\n打手團滿口歪理，積腐於腸口噴糞！</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n今日我請在座咁多位網民陪審團見證我屌柒呢班人間渣滓<br />\n陳詞內容皆有實質證據及圖片佐證，<br />\n客觀證明連尼住同你班狗，係仆街冚家剷！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>連登歪風不絕，搞意識形態操控</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n連登成立短短一年，連登仔比外界嘅形象卑劣<br />\n年紀輕輕，思想淫穢至極，不識邏輯情理。<br />\n眾人皆曰可殺。<br />\n<br />\n連尼住用熱門、打手團、篤數正負皮，控制人接觸嘅資訊<br />\n荼毒香港青年思想，搞到歪風不絕，人格敗壞。<br />\n<br />\n令人痛恨嘅係，<br />\n連登吸納咗大量中小學生，<br />\n一但敗壞嘅種子植根於青年思想<br />\n後果堪虞，禍延後代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證據：<br />\n【核彈一號】連登　賤過Baby Kingdom / 5P壇嘅有力證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6791109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6791109&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0d386d5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6791109</a> <br />\n<br />\n【深入調查】連登　意識形態操控　人流造假　資料整合 (二)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6767871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6767871&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e750a63d\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6767871</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>打手挑動連登、高登兩派對立 打散網路力量</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港本土派之興起、對抗極權之志，始流於網路，<br />\n高登曾經係一道洪水，聚民之志，擁智之理。<br />\n一直係極權者嘅眼中釘。<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街連衛兵，成日係度屌高登仔盲從，<br />\n挑動雙方對立面，搞共產黨開國四寶：群眾鬥群眾<br />\n打散網路力量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證據：<br />\n查冊買股票 2 - 另一間紅色連登概念股 蔡素玉&amp;政協加持<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6782974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6782974&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7aceef07\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6782974</a> <br />\n<br />\n【有智之士入嚟】面對中共網路統戰　高登仔同連登仔必須作出訣擇<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6782153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6782153&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=54f59882\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6782153</a>"},{"pid":"e121aa117426573212b4753e768595e240c38ecf","tid":492064,"uid":32826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>連狗BAM人、DEL POST、輿論導向之快　無人能及</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔知連狗公司有幾多打手團，幾多人做嘢。<br />\n但最撚奇怪嘅係，同一個事件，兩種處理方法：<br />\n<br />\n廢Joe曾經拎成百幾萬打官司去維護「網路言論自由」<br />\n最後敗訴，要Bam人 Del Post。<br />\n連登仔都屌撚到阿Joe仆街。<br />\n<br />\n連尼住一收到 「Email 律師信」<br />\n就Bam人 Del Post。<br />\n就有一大班連衛兵幫佢護短？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乜撚嘢道理呀孽畜？！</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n果班俾係LIHKG俾人BAM 嘅會員，<br />\n以前發過嘅POST 同 留言<br />\n全部都DEL哂，<br />\n不留痕跡，人間蒸發。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乜撚嘢言論自由呀？！</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 乜撚嘢全港最自由論壇呀</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n你班仆街打手仲好意思提，乜撚嘢613 女夜鬼事件<br />\n知唔知個醜字點寫呀？<br />\n你班孽畜真係毫無羞恥之心。<br />\n個口噴緊屎都唔識自漸形穢！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到呢度，正如我開頭所講，<br />\n人禽之辨，在於明辨是非。<br />\n聰明人自然會有聰明嘅選擇，<br />\n到而家都仲幫連尼主做連衛兵嘅<br />\n你都係孽畜嚟，返連登啦仆街！<br />\n<br />\n如果有打手覺得我上面講得唔啱，<br />\n不服來辨。擔定札<br />\n但辨論，唔該你班打手比啲水準<br />\n咪撚搞文革式標籤，咪撚搞形式主義<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冚家剷！公理係要事實佐證嫁仆街！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2feaab9e3108164bf6fddc661cb2f99114ba5a20","tid":492064,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"講到似層層, 有冇Evidence先?<br />\n我淨係知高登熱狗多到仆街, 返去就咪搞喇? 連登有事大不了咪唔上<br />\n<br />\n利申, 呢個acc 借人用"},{"pid":"12bb10b69e159952e04b732166e3142a86086ed8","tid":492064,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}